title: 3 bedroom 2 bath house bayside boarder
posting_body: ['Off 29 ave and 163 street', 'House for rent, sunny, spacious, close to train and highways, dishwasher, laundry, rear yard/deck and garage', 'Move into this beautiful house and enjoy the convenience of being close to all transportation and shopping.', 'Your own yard, garage and driveway!', 'Minutes from the Clearview/Cross Island Pkwys and bridges.', 'Close to the Bay Terrace Shopping Center.', 'Just a few blocks to the LIRR  station.', 'Large dining room and living room offer plenty of room to stretch out and relax.', 'Hardwood floors and high ceilings.', 'Gorgeous eat-in kitchen with abundant counter space and dishwasher.', 'The master bedroom easily holds a king-size bed.', 'Second bedroom fits a queen-sized bed and furniture.', 'Master bathroom with tub and separate shower.', 'Enjoy the summer entertaining or relaxing in your back yard.', 'Front patio too.', 'Laundry downstairs.', 'Utilities not included broker 7186071117']
